N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 603.6 - Exhibits

State Regulations

Attached to the petition shall be certified copies of
official ordinances or resolutions authorizing the application and the signing
thereof and any other such acts in connection with the matter, together with
any pertinent maps, reports or papers which applicant may desire to
submit. Notes
